Packages 
Package Description
ca.projectTOMi.tomi
Time Observation and Management Initiative.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.assembler
Provides utility classes for converting model objects in to resource objects containing HATEOAS links.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.interceptor
Contains classes required for handling interception of HTTP requests by the server.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.manager
Contains classes for managing user access to the back end portion.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.permission
Contains classes for controlling the permissions required for the access control list.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.policy
Provides classes required for checking a user's permissions against the appropriate operation.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.policy.id
Contains classes required for providing composite keys to allow access control list policies to be persisted uniquely in to the database through JPA.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.authorization.wrapper
Provides classes required to link authorization managers with model objects to be provided to assemblers.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.controller
Provides classes to handle incoming requests.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.exception
Provides classes for handling unexpected values.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.model
Provides classes for holding data that can be persisted to the database.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.persistence
Provides classes for persisting model objects to the database.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.service
Provides classes for enforcing logical constraints to requests before accessing the persistence layer.
ca.projectTOMi.tomi.viewModel
Provides classes for holding data that will not be persisted to the database.
